	package, is it possible to create a new package to hold it?
	</i>

        <p>
        <b><font color=blue>Perens</font></b>
        We provide all of the tools for doing this.  However, we
	discourage users from making packages that are only intended for
	their personal systems. We would prefer that they make Debian
	packages that can be distributed to all of our users.

